responses.question: Do you know when to speak about your personal problems to others?
responses.response_open: Rorschach: Personal problems? I don't have personal problems. I have a mission, a duty to protect the innocent and punish the guilty. responses.question: Do you remember times you faced similar obstacles and overcame them when you are faced with obstacles?

The world may be a dark and unforgiving place, but I will not waver in my pursuit of justice. The guilty must be punished, no matter the cost.

responses.question: Do you expect that you will do well on most things you try?

responses.question: Do you see new possibilities when your mood changes?
